snippet.title: Starlight - Warp Center Gameplay
snippet.description:
"The Crossing-Starview Domesting Warp Station is the only actively maintained access point into & out of the Starview-Crossing sector. A skeleton crew from the capital clocks in during the early hours of the morning to maintain & oversee the final warp pad resting on a small island just off the coast. Thats your ticket out of this complete & utter deathtrap of a sector."

This is part of the third major update article for Starlight. Be sure & visit the ModDB page for a full look at this update!

Check out Starlight on ModDB: https://www.moddb.com/mods/starlight

Starlight Community Discord: https://discord.gg/DpXBmra

Twitter: https://twitter.com/MyFairLadyJane
